                                                <div class="megadropdown-text-box">
                                                    <p><strong>The European Council</strong></p>
<p>The European Council is the EU institution that defines the general political direction and priorities of the European Union. It consists of the <strong>heads of state or government of the member states</strong>, together with its President and the President of the Commission. </p>


