    <h2>
        <a class="highlited-item-title-link" href="/en/council-eu/presidency-council-eu/" itemprop="url">&#39;Together for Europe&#39;s recovery&#39;: Germany takes over Council presidency</a>
    </h2>
    <p class="highlited-item-title-text">
        <p>1 July 2020 marks the beginning of Germany’s presidency of the Council of the EU. The presidency will focus on how to support Europe's recovery from the COVID-19 pandemic. The presidency's objective is for Europe to emerge stronger, more sustainable and more just from this crisis.</p>
    </p>

