            <div class="message-box">
                


    




<p>The <strong>General Secretariat of the Council</strong> is a body of staff responsible for assisting the European Council and the Council of the EU. It helps organise and ensure the coherence of the Council's work and the implementation of its 18-month programme.</p>



















